description:

01. Matt Darey feat. Bonse - This Way (Matt Darey Mix)
02. Nic Chagall - What you Need (Original Mix)
03. Matt Darey v Tall Paul feat. Alabama 3 - No Submission (Matt Darey Tech Mix)
04. Luetzenkirchen - The Killer
05. Quivver Vs. Audio Magnetics - Digital Music (Seth Vogt Remix)
06. Coburn - Razorblade (Play Paul Club remix)
07. Tronso & StianKio - Sodium Lamp (Virus J & DJ Sun Remix)
08. The Doppler Effect - Beauty Hides in the Deep (Envotion remix)
09. 68 Beats - Replay The Night (Gabriel & Dresden mix)
10. DYAD10 feat. Julie Dennis - Sugar (Sweet Thing) (Tocadisco Mix)
11. Matt Darey feat. Tiff Lacey - Sum of all Fears (Matt Darey Mix)
12. Julian Jeweil - Air Conditionne (Original Mix)
13. Super8 & Tab - Need To Feel (Wippenberg Remix)


Matt Darey first made a name for himself as the DJ / A&R on the famous Euphoria mix CD series, which ran between 2000 and 2005 and those volumes which featured his name as the mix DJ sold almost 2 million copies in the UK alone.
After establishing himself further as an elite-league DJ / dance producer with several UK chart hits of his own, he now presents 'NOCTURNAL', one of the most widely broadcasted dance radio shows globally on 114 stations weekly. The energy of his popular DJ radio show is superbly captured on this CD, showcasing his unique blend of House, Electro, Progressive, Trance and Breakbeats.
